Description: # logger_rewrite
        Easy way to log everything
        ### Install
        ```bash
        pip install logult
        ```
        
        ### Use
        ```
        from logult import setup_log
        logger=  setup_log(save_dir='saved', name_exp='info.log')
        logger.info('Hello')
        ```
        
